OL,3,CCritically ill girl has lifesaving
OL,4,Coperation to fit 'Berlin heart'
OL,6,FThe parents of a seriously ill baby
OL,7,Ffrom Whitby say "Christmas has come
OL,8,Fearly" after their little girl
OL,9,Freceived the life-saving operation she
OL,10,Fneeded.
OL,12,FFourteen-month-old Penelope Greathead
OL,13,Fwas living on borrowed time at Leeds
OL,14,FChildren's Hospital after a cardiac
OL,15,Farrest three weeks ago.
