OL,3,CCritically ill girl has lifesaving
OL,4,Coperation to fit 'Berlin heart'
OL,6,FShe was hooked up to a machine which
OL,7,Fwould only temporarily keep her heart
OL,8,Fgoing, and needed an operation to fit
OL,9,Fa 'Berlin Heart' which could sustain
OL,10,Fher in the longer term while she waits
OL,11,Ffor a heart donor.
OL,13,FBut her mum and dad, Holly and Jordan
OL,14,Fwere delivered the devastating news
OL,15,Fthat there were no beds available in
OL,16,Fthe two hospitals which could provide
OL,17,Fthe specialist care she needed.
