OL,3,CCritically ill girl has lifesaving
OL,4,Coperation to fit 'Berlin heart'
OL,6,FNHS England says beds for children
OL,7,Fwith similar heart conditions are in
OL,8,Fhigh demand because donors are so hard
OL,9,Fto find.
OL,11,FSpeaking to Calendar earlier this
OL,12,Fmonth Holly said: "This is a funding
OL,13,Fissue and it sounds like it's such a
OL,14,Fsimple thing to save our little girl's
OL,15,Flife. This is why we want to raise
OL,16,Fawareness because there are others in
OL,17,Fthis position as well.'"
