OL,3,CCritically ill girl has lifesaving
OL,4,Coperation to fit 'Berlin heart'
OL,6,FDetermined to get their daughter the
OL,7,Fsurgery she needed, the couple
OL,8,Flaunched a fundraising campaign to pay
OL,9,Ffor treatment abroad, and raised
OL,10,F#120,000 over the space of a weekend.
OL,12,FBut just last week a bed unexpectedly
OL,13,Fbecame available at Great Ormond
OL,14,FStreet Hospital, and Penelope was
OL,15,Ftaken from Leeds Children's Hospital
OL,16,Fto London by ambulance. On Friday 20th
OL,17,FDecember she underwent the life-saving
OL,18,Foperation.
