OL,3,CCritically ill girl has lifesaving
OL,4,Coperation to fit 'Berlin heart'
OL,6,F"Everything went well" Jordan said.
OL,7,F"It's still early days in her recovery
OL,8,Fand this journey but it's great she is
OL,9,Ffinally off (life support)."
OL,11,FPenelope's parents will now donate the
OL,12,Fmoney they raised to heart charities,
OL,13,Fand plan to start their own.
