OL,3,CCritically ill girl has lifesaving
OL,4,Coperation to fit 'Berlin heart'
OL,6,FJordan said: "Children with Berlin
OL,7,FHearts fitted have to remain in
OL,8,Fhospital until they receive a donor
OL,9,Fheart. She could be in Great Ormond
OL,10,FStreet for up to two years waiting for
OL,11,Fthis. Raising awareness about the
OL,12,Fimportance and impact of organ
OL,13,Fdonation is key to her future."
